description:
&nbsp;This repository contains CellProfiler pipelines and associated analysis workflows used in the study: " Developing a Protocol to Counteract Spontaneous In Vitro Activation of Intestinal Fibroblasts Using Design of Experiments" .  The repository includes:&nbsp; 

 CellProfiler pipelines for quantifying &alpha;-SMA, FAP, Vinculin, and cell counts 
 Image-analysis workflows for fluorescence microscopy data 
 CSV-based quantitative output workflows 
 Documentation for pipeline execution and downstream analysis 

 This release was archived through Zenodo to support reproducibility and citation of the analysis workflows used in the manuscript.&nbsp;

